Class AbstractComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ghost4j.AbstractComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Component
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractAnalyzer, AbstractConverter, AbstractModifier, AbstractRemoteComponent, AbstractRenderer

    public abstract class AbstractComponent
extends Object
implements Component
    Abstract component implementation. Contains methods that are common to the different component types (converter, analyzer, modifier ...)
    Author:
    Gilles Grousset (gi.grousset@gmail.com)
